  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink26-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> talaimakaṟku vāyilākap pukuntār, ‘niṉ muṉiviṟku avaṉ poruntā niṉṟāṉ’ eṉṟa
          vaḻit talaimakaṭkut tōḻi, ‘avaṉ pāṭu aḵtillai’ eṉpatupaṭac colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink26">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          karantaiyañ ceṟuviṟ ṟuṇaituṟantu kaḷvaṉ</l>
<l>          vaḷḷai meṉkā laṟukku mūra</l>
<l>          ṉemmum piṟaru maṟiyā</l>
<l>          ṉiṉṉa ṉāva tevaṉko laṉṉāy.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>          The man from the village</l>
<l rend="indent2">          where the crab, having abandoned [its] mate in the thistle fields,</l>
<l rend="indent2">          tears off the soft bindweed stalks</l>
<l>        doesn't know us nor anyone else.</l>
<l>        That he is like this: What [of it], mother?</l>
        


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
